  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    UK in India: Pledge for Progress
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">British High Commission in New Delhi launched 'Pledge for Progress' campaign with partners across India to promote gender equality and mobilise real change. </p>

  </div>
</div>

